<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>For Yalzz ❤️</title>

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
}

body{
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff8fb8,#ffd6e7);
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
height:100vh;
overflow:hidden;
}

.card{
width:90%;
max-width:400px;
background:#fff;
padding:30px;
border-radius:20px;
box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
text-align:center;
position:relative;
animation:pop .5s ease;
}

@keyframes pop{
from{
transform:scale(.8);
opacity:0;
}
to{
transform:scale(1);
opacity:1;
}
}

h1{
color:#ff3b7a;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

p{
font-size:18px;
line-height:1.8;
color:#333;
}

button{
margin-top:25px;
padding:12px 28px;
font-size:18px;
border:none;
border-radius:12px;
background:#ff3b7a;
color:white;
cursor:pointer;
transition:.3s;
}

button:hover{
transform:scale(1.05);
}

.page{
display:none;
}

.active{
display:block;
}

.heart{
position:absolute;
color:#ff3b7a;
animation:float 6s linear infinite;
opacity:.6;
}

@keyframes float{
0%{
transform:translateY(100vh);
}
100%{
transform:translateY(-120vh);
}
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="card">

<div id="page1" class="page active">

<h1>Hi Yalzz ❤️</h1>

<p>

Indha website-a open pannadhukku thanks. ❤️

<br><br>

Nee dhan enoda lucky charm pah! 💕

<br><br>

Nee vandhadhuku aprm dhan naan
Sanchana-va marandhu
unkuda sandhoshama irundhen.

<br><br>

Aana...

namma sanda potadhum
yen andha akka kitta pesunen nu
enakke therla.

<br><br>

Adhukku manasaara sorry. 😔

</p>

<button onclick="nextPage(2)">Next ➜</button>

</div>
<div id="page2" class="page">

<h1>Yalzz... ❤️</h1>

<p>

Naan panadhu thappu dhaan...
Adha naan othukuren.

<br><br>

Inime andha thappa
oru naalum repeat panna maten.

<br><br>

Un trust-ah dhaan
en life-la romba mukkiyama paakuren.

<br><br>

Adha kandippa kaapathuven. 💯

<br><br>

Idhuku apram
unnakitta poi solli
unnai hurt panna maten.

<br><br>

Indha oru vaati
enna nambu.

<br><br>

Enoda motha love-um,
care-um,
future-um...
unakku dhaan. 🤌🏻💕❣️

</p>

<button onclick="nextPage(3)">Next ➜</button>

</div>

<div id="page3" class="page">

<h1>One Last Thing... ❤️</h1>

<p>

Unna lose panna
enakku viruppam illa.

<br><br>

Indha oru thadava
enna mannichidu.

<br><br>

Thirumba enakku
innoru chance kudu pahh.

<br><br>

Unakaga dhaan
naan kathukitte iruken. 🤌🏻🫠

<br><br>

Please... ❤️

</p>

<h2 style="margin-top:20px;color:#ff3b7a;">
Will You Give Me One More Chance
<br>
and Be My Girlfriend? 💍❤️
</h2>

<button onclick="yes()">YES 💖</button>

<button id="noBtn">NO 😅</button>

</div>
</div>

<script>

function nextPage(page){
document.querySelectorAll(".page").forEach(p=>{
p.classList.remove("active");
});
document.getElementById("page"+page).classList.add("active");
}

function yes(){

document.body.innerHTML=`

<div style="height:100vh;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff8fb8,#ffd6e7);
font-family:Arial;
text-align:center;
padding:20px;">

<div>

<h1 style="color:#ff3b7a;font-size:38px;">
🥹❤️ Thank You Yalzz ❤️🥹
</h1>

<p style="font-size:22px;margin-top:20px;line-height:1.8;">

You made me the happiest person. 💕

<br><br>

I Promise...

I'll never break your trust again.

🤞🏻❤️

</p>

</div>

</div>

`;

}

const no=document.getElementById("noBtn");

no.addEventListener("mouseover",()=>{

no.style.position="absolute";
no.style.left=Math.random()*70+"%";
no.style.top=Math.random()*70+"%";

});

for(let i=0;i<30;i++){

let h=document.createElement("div");

h.className="heart";

h.innerHTML="❤️";

h.style.left=Math.random()*100+"%";

h.style.animationDuration=(Math.random()*5+5)+"s";

h.style.fontSize=(Math.random()*20+15)+"px";

document.body.appendChild(h);

}

</script>

</body>

</html>
